jQuery is basically a framework/library which we can use in our code to make it easier

$->THIS SIGN IS USED IN PLACE OF document.querySelector

#how to include jquery
 <script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/3.7.0/jquery.min.js"></script>

#sample code in JS

$("h1").css("color","red");

#we can use a minifier to shorten our code
